e [[population density]] was 24.87 inhabitants per km\u00b2. [[Inkere]] was the [[administrative center]] of Pertteli.\n\nThe municipality was unilingually [[Finnish language|Finnish]].\n\n[[Bartholomew the Apostle|Saint Bartholomew]] is the [[namesake]] of the municipality and is the subject of the [[Heraldry|heraldic shield]].\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category-inline}}\n*http://www.pertteli.fi/ \u2013 Official website {{in lang|fi}}\n\n{{FinlandProper}}\n\n{{coord|60|26|50|N|23|14|55|E|region:FI_type:city(3934)_scale:50000|display=title}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Former municipalities of Finland]]\n[[Category:Salo, Finland]]\n[[Category:Populated places disestablished in 2009]]\n[[Category:2009 disestablishments in Finland]]\n\n\n{{WesternFinland-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Pertteli\n| official_name           = {{lang|fi|Perttelin kunta}}<br />{{lang|sv|S:t Bertils kommun}}\n| native_name             = {{lang|fi|Pertteli}} \u2013 {{lang|sv|S:t Bertils}}\n| native_name_lang        = <!-- ISO 639-2 code. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead  -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Finland|Former municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_flag              = \n| flag_alt                = \n| image_seal              = \n| seal_alt                = \n| image_shield            = Pertteli.vaakuna.svg\n| shield_alt              = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| image_map               = Pertteli.sijainti.suomi.2008.svg\n| map_alt                 = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = <!-- Finland -->\n| pushpin_label_position  = right\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location within Finland\n| coordinates             = \n| coor_pinpoint           = \n| coo